updateAlternative

public java.util.Vector<RationaleStatus> updateAlternative(Alternative alt)
Performs updates needed when something has happened that might affect the status of an alternative. This could mean an argument has changed, or some other rationale element that connects to an alterantive (like a question or requirement)
